===Etymology===
Cognate with {{och-l|洟}}, and along with it, traditionally derived from {{inh|zh|sit-pro|*m-t(w)əj-n ~ m-ti-s||water}} and compared with {{cog|bo|མཆི་མ|t=tears}} ({{zh-ref|Schuessler, 2007}}). However, based on the Baxter-Sagart reconstruction, note stronger resemblance to {{cog|sit-pro|*rəj|t=water; liquid; body fluid}}, whence {{cog|my|ရေ|t=water}}.

